  "description": "A nighttime cityscape featuring two prominent bridges, likely in San Francisco, California. The foreground showcases a modern suspension bridge illuminated with bright white lights, creating a striking contrast against the dark water below. Behind it, the iconic Bay Bridge is visible, adorned with a line of lights. The city skyline in the background is densely packed with illuminated buildings, including a particularly tall skyscraper glowing with a purple hue. Firework displays are visible above the city, adding bursts of color to the dark sky. The overall scene is a dynamic and vibrant representation of urban life at night.",
